---
const points = ['Competitive pricing', 'Reliable service', 'Local expertise in Braj'];
---

<section id="about" class="scroll-mt-20 border-t border-braj-sand bg-white py-14 sm:py-20">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6">
		<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-10 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between">
			<div class="max-w-xl">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-braj-blue sm:text-3xl">We are Braj Go Tour and Travels</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 text-braj-blue/90">
					Mathura Vrindavan tour packages let you experience the sacred land in the most cost-effective way. We offer tours to temples and heritage sites with comfortable stays and a range of vehicles to fit your group and budget.
				</p>
				<ul class="mt-6 space-y-2">
					{points.map((p) => (
						<li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-braj-blue/90">
							<span class="text-braj-green">âœ“</span>
							<span>{p}</span>
						</li>
					))}
				</ul>
				<div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
					<a href="tel:9228597072" class="rounded-lg bg-braj-blue px-6 py-3 font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-braj-blue/90">Call now</a>
					<a href="#packages" class="rounded-lg border border-braj-blue px-6 py-3 font-semibold text-braj-blue transition hover:bg-braj-blue/10">Learn more</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="flex h-48 w-48 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-braj-sand/60">
				<span class="font-serif text-4xl font-semibold text-braj-blue/50">BRAJ GO</span>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
